snippet.title: Fellow Commanders!
snippet.description:
Fellow Commanders! Be on your toes for news in the coming weeks and months.

Official Site / Download: https://wz2100.net/
Official Discord / Webchat: https://wz2100.net/webchat/

Made by LupusMechanicus and Pastdue, using Kdenlive, footage from the game's cutscenes and aks1on's glitch footage, which you can find it here:
https://youtu.be/KNepwnVWfdg

Kudos to Phase II for upscaling the cutscenes. ;)
